These figures are for MyPay LTD and MyPay PSC LTD. Supporting Statement    What our contractors say:    I have been a member of MyPay for over a year. The service I have received has been of a very high standard  Adam Lound     I will gladly recommend this service to anyone interested in setting up his own company, as it gives you more or less the same benefits with fewer hassles  Dr Nischol Raval     I have worked for two years now and have been thoroughly satisfied with the service and assistance I have received  Nigel Lewin      I have always been 100% happy with the service I receive from MyPay  Julie Bullimore      I would not hesitate in recommending MyPay to anyone as I have been very grateful for all the help they have given me.  Martin Tanner         html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd"                  html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd"     Copyright Â© 2012 MyPay | Sitemap | Site by DRP Creative Limited   